vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of a utility easement to BCIF Oakdale Logistics Center LLC, the abutting owner, containing approximately 157,176 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Singleton Boulevard and Weir Street - Revenue: General Fund $7,800.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
